	Modify _AC_PATH_X_XMKMF and _AC_PATH_X_DIRECT, adding "dylib"
	(for Mac OS X) and "dll" (Cygwin) to suffix lists.  These macros
	depend on finding the exact filename for libX11 (if xmkmf exists
